*lxc-1.1.0-r5 (14 Mar 2015)

  14 Mar 2015; Markos Chandras <hwoarang@gentoo.org> +lxc-1.1.0-r5.ebuild:
  Move tools from sbin to bin so we can start supporting unprivileged containers

